Sequence Information.Family: Belongs to the frog skin active peptide family (Brevinin subfamily)
Sequence Information.Target Organism: Gram-positive bacterium:Staphylococcus aureus (MIC=15 µM);Gram-negative bacterium:Escherichia coli (MIC=119 µM).
Sequence Information.Hemolytic Activity: No hemolysis information or data found in the reference(s) presented in this entry
Sequence Information.Comments: It can produced cell death of mammalian COS7 cells (LD50=28 µM).

Literature.Title: Molecular cloning of a cDNA encoding atypical antimicrobial and cytotoxic brevinin-1Ja from the skin of the Japanese brown frog, Rana japonica.
Literature.Author: Koyama T, Iwamuro S.
